content: That's really helpful, thanks! I'll definitely give those recipes a try. I've been meaning to experiment with different protein powders too, so it's great that you mentioned that. By the way, I stopped by the convenience store on my way home from work on Monday and ended up buying a bag of chips and a soda, which wasn't the healthiest choice. But I'm trying to get back on track now. Do you have any tips on how to avoid those kinds of impulse buys in the future?
